# Evolution of Maintenance Strategy 

&mdash; maintenance strategies is evolved(in good way) from time to time. 

it triggered by academics findings or event from some noteable accident. For example, the latest maintenance strategy called as a RCM(reliability centered mainteance) was born on 1968 because high accident on aviation industry specifically at that year.  Below are the timeline of maintenance strategies

1. reactive maintenance (then)
2. time based maintenance
3. preventive maintenance
4. performance based maintenance
5. condition based maintenance
6. reliability based maintenance (recent)

lower order means the most recent maintenance strategies (most up to date)

## Reliability Centered Maintenance (RCM)